---
title: Cheesy Beef Rissoles & Potato Wedges with Caramelised Onion & Mixed Salad
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing winner, but when you cover them with cheese and sweet caramelised onion, they’re even harder to refuse! This colourful plate also gets a serve of wedges and a family-friendly salad for a rainbow of delights.

